{"lemma":"حِدْثانِ","slug":"حِدْثانِ","root":"ح.د.ث","root_slug":"ح-د-ث","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-د-ث","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7319","n7320"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%90%D8%AF%D9%92%D8%AB%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of حَدَث (ḥadaṯ)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of حَدِيث (ḥadīṯ)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7319","headword_ar":"حِدْثَانٌ","root":"Hdv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beginning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commencement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a state, or a case, or an affair; (S, A, Mgh, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadaAvapN","text_ar":"حَدَاثَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Mgh, K:) and its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"freshness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is also a signification of both these words. (S, Mgh.) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifoEalo *`lika AlA^amora biHidovaAnihi","text_ar":"اِفْعَلْ ذٰلِكَ الاَمْرَ بِحِدْثَانِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biHadaAvatihi","text_ar":"بِحَدَاثَتِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do thou that thing while it is in its first and fresh state"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, Mgh. *) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu fiY HidovaAni $abaAbihi","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ فِى حِدْثَانِ شَبَابِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$bAbh","text_ar":"شبابه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HidovaY","text_ar":"حِدْثَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$bAbh","text_ar":"شبابه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hadiyvi","text_ar":"حَدِيثِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him in the beginning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first period, of his youth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-'Amr Esh-Sheybánee, TA.) And it is said in a trad., addressed to 'Áïsheh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawolaA","text_ar":"لَوْلَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HidovaAnu qawomiki biAlkufori lahadamotu AlkaEobapa wabanayotuhaA","text_ar":"حِدْثَانُ قَوْمِكِ بِالكُفْرِ لَهَدَمْتُ الكَعْبَةَ وَبَنَيْتُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, * TA,) or, as some relate it,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qwmk","text_ar":"قومك"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadaAvapu","text_ar":"حَدَاثَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which means the same, (Mgh,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Were it not for the shortness of the period that has elapsed since thy people were in the state of infidelity, I would pull down the Kaabeh, and build it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[anew]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadavN","text_ar":"حَدَثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K"]},{"entry_id":"n7320","headword_ar":"حَدَثَانٌ","root":"Hdv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", used as a sing. and as a pl.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HdvN","text_ar":"حدثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."},{"kind":"page_break","n":529}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}